data.description: Under contract-accepting backup offers. This is country living at its finest!! Check out this beautiful 2,100+ SqFt, 3 bed 2 bath, 1 car attached carport manufactured home nestled on 1+ acre. Arriving on the property, you are welcomed into a parklike setting adorned with  mature oaks and an expansive yard with plenty of space for a garden and fruit orchard.  Step into the open concept family room kitchen that creates that special blend of relaxing and socializing. In the family room cozy up by the crackling fireplace on chilly evenings, creating the perfect ambiance for relaxation and warmth. The spacious kitchen is a chef's delight, equipped with stainless steel appliances, plenty of cabinet space, a walk-in pantry and a breakfast bar that's perfect for hosting unforgettable parties that flow into the dining area. The master bedroom is spacious and the en-suite includes dual sinks, a walk-in shower, a garden tub and a large walk-in closet. Completing the living space are two secondary bedrooms, a full-sized bathroom and a large laundry room. Sit outdoors on the screened lanai and enjoy the sounds of nature with a morning cup of coffee. With no HOA or CDD, the oversized property with a detached carport provides ample room for parking a RV, boat, and all the toys! A 2 car barn/workshop with a lean to chicken coop is the ideal place to tinker! With a short distance to shopping and dining, this location offers both convenience and tranquility. Don't miss out on the chance to own this sanctuary of peace and quiet!. Schedule your showing TODAY!!
